%% Diagram: Akkio microshard access tracking, placement scoring, and migration
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Application client
    participant AC as Akkio client
    participant Loc as Location DB
    participant Acc as Access counter DB
    participant DPS as Data placement service
    participant Src as Source data centre
    participant Dst as Target data centre

    App->>AC: read/write μ-shard X
    AC->>Loc: lookup placement(X)
    Loc-->>AC: placement P (DC list)
    AC->>Src: forward request to local replica in P
    AC->>Acc: async record access(X, region)

    Note over AC,DPS: Cross-region access detected
    AC-->>DPS: hint: μ-shard X is suboptimally placed

    DPS->>Acc: read 3-day access history(X)
    DPS->>DPS: score regions by recency × capacity
    alt new placement P' wins
        DPS->>Loc: acquire migration lock(X)
        DPS->>Src: set source ACL = read-only
        DPS->>Dst: copy μ-shard X
        DPS->>Loc: atomically update placement → P'
        DPS->>Src: delete μ-shard X
        DPS->>Loc: release lock
    else current placement still optimal
        DPS-->>AC: no-op
    end
